claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table summarizing demographic and clinical characteristics (sex, race/ethnicity, Hispanic ethnicity, coexisting illnesses, and prior-year influenza vaccination) of study participants who received either a recombinant vaccine or a standard-dose vaccine. The table contains only participant demographics and clinical history; it provides no data on antigenic match with WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains and therefore does not support the claim.
